dc_title_s: School Board District Boundaries: Prince George's County, Maryland
dc_description_s: To show the current boundaries of the Prince George's County School Board. The boundaries are defined and its representation approved by the Board of Elections. This coverage is not suitable for identification of individual parcels. COVERAGE DERIVATION: This coverage was originally developed for the Board of Elections mapping project and presents the boundaries of the School Board. Updates are received from the Prince George's County Office of Information Technology.
dc_creator_sm: Prince George's County Office of Information Technology - GIS
